@startuml Statistics Flow

actor Admin
participant "AdminDashboard (UI)" as UI
participant "StatisticsController" as Controller
participant "StatisticsService" as Service
participant "StatisticsRepository" as Repository
database "MongoDB" as DB

Admin -> UI: Click "Thống kê" tab
UI -> Controller: GET /api/statistics/top-sales
Controller -> Service: getTopSellingProducts(limit)
Service -> Repository: getTopProductsBySoldCount(limit)
Repository -> DB: Product.find().sort({soldCount: -1}).limit(limit)
DB --> Repository: Result (List of products)
Repository --> Service: List of products
Service --> Controller: Formatted stats data
Controller --> UI: JSON Response {status: 'success', data: [...]}
UI --> Admin: Display Statistics Table/Charts

@enduml
